`\n- `models/*.py` (henüz boş ama birazdan dolduracağız)\n\nBu komutlar bittiğinde **“tamam”** de; hemen ADIM 2.1’e geçip dosyaları dolduracağız.\n\n---\n\n## ADIM 2.1 — requirements.txt + .gitignore + settings + database (DOLDURMA)\n\nADIM 2.0 tamam olunca, Copilot’a şu tek talimatı vereceksin (VS Code/Copilot editör tarafında da olur):\n\n### Copilot’a ver (dosyaları yazdıracağız)\n\u003e “Aşağıdaki dosyaları içerikleriyle oluştur/doldur. Hiçbir ekstra paket ekleme. Hiçbir dosyayı atlama.”\n\nBen içerikleri bir sonraki mesajda vereceğim (çok uzun olacağı için ADIM 2.0 tamam cevabını bekliyorum).\n\n---\n\n## Şimdi Senden Tek Şey İstiyorum\nADIM 2.0 komutlarını çalıştır ve buraya sadece şunu yaz:\n\n1) `find . -type f | sort` çıktısı (kısa da olsa)  \n2) Hata olduysa hata metni\n\nSonra ben **ADIM 2.1 için**:\n- `requirements.txt` (minimum)\n- `.gitignore`\n- `config/settings.py` (env yükleyici + validate)\n- `core/modules/database.py` (tablolar + create_tables + health_check)\n- `memory/agent_memory.py` (agent karar kayıt/okuma)\n\ndosyalarının final içeriklerini tek tek vereceğim ve kurulum ilerleyecek."])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"22:T3e67,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"ADIM 2.1’e geçiyoruz: **konfig + log + PostgreSQL (SQLAlchemy) + hafıza katmanı**.  \nHenüz tarama/haber/telegram komutlarını yazmıyoruz; önce altyapı “ayağa kalkacak” ve DB tabloları oluşacak.\n\nAşağıdaki tek komutu Copilot’a ver (Oracle terminal). Bu komut **dosyaları eksiksiz doldurur**, gereksiz hiçbir şey eklemez.\n\n---\n\n## ADIM 2.1 — Copilot Terminal Komutu (tek parça)\n\n```bash\ncd ~/trading_ai_system\n\n# scheduler.py bu mimaride kullanılmayacak (plan: core/orchestrator/event_manager.py)\nrm -f scheduler.py\n\n# gerekli __init__.py'ler\nmkdir -p core/modules core/orchestrator interfaces models memory config tests logs\ntouch core/modules/__init__.py core/orchestrator/__init__.py interfaces/__init__.py models/__init__.py\n\n# .gitignore\ncat \u003e .gitignore \u003c\u003c'EOF'\n# Secrets\nconfig/api_keys.env\n*.env\n\n# Python\n__pycache__/\n*.py[cod]\nvenv/\n.env/\n.venv/\n\n# IDE\n.vscode/\n.idea/\n\n# Logs\nlogs/\nEOF\n\n# requirements.txt (minimum + ihtiyaçlarımız)\ncat \u003e requirements.txt \u003c\u003c'EOF'\npython-telegram-bot==21.3\npandas==2.2.2\nnumpy==1.26.4\nrequests==2.32.3\nfeedparser==6.0.11\n\nsqlalchemy==2.0.31\npsycopg2-binary==2.9.9\n\napscheduler==3.10.4\n\npython-dotenv==1.0.1\npyyaml==6.0.1\nloguru==0.7.2\n\ngoogle-generativeai==0.7.2\ngroq==0.9.0\nEOF\n\n# config/api_keys.env (şablon)\ncat \u003e config/api_keys.env \u003c\u003c'EOF'\n# Telegram\nTELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=\nTELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=\n\n# AI\nGEMINI_API_KEY=\nGROQ_API_KEY=\n\n# PostgreSQL\nDB_HOST=localhost\nDB_PORT=5432\nDB_NAME=trading_ai\nDB_USER=\nDB_PASSWORD=\nEOF\n\n# config/settings.py\ncat \u003e config/settings.py \u003c\u003c'EOF'\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport os\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\nimport yaml\nfrom loguru import logger\n\nBASE_DIR = Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent\n\n# Load env\nENV_PATH = BASE_DIR / \"config\" / \"api_keys.env\"\nload_dotenv(dotenv_path=ENV_PATH)\n\nclass Settings:\n    _instance = None\n    _config: dict\n\n    def __new__(cls):\n        if cls._instance is None:\n            cls._instance = super().__new__(cls)\n            cls._instance._load_yaml()\n        return cls._instance\n\n    def _load_yaml(self):\n        cfg_path = BASE_DIR / \"config\" / \"agents_config.yaml\"\n        if not cfg_path.exists():\n            self._config = {}\n            return\n        try:\n            self._config = yaml.safe_load(cfg_path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\")) or {}\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"agents_config.yaml okunamadı: {e}\")\n            self._config = {}\n\n    # ENV\n    @property\n    def telegram_bot_token(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\", \"\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def telegram_chat_id(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID\", \"\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def gemini_api_key(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"GEMINI_API_KEY\", \"\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def groq_api_key(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"GROQ_API_KEY\", \"\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def db_host(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"DB_HOST\", \"localhost\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def db_port(self) -\u003e int:\n        return int(os.getenv(\"DB_PORT\", \"5432\").strip())\n\n    @property\n    def db_name(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"DB_NAME\", \"trading_ai\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def db_user(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"DB_USER\", \"\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def db_password(self) -\u003e str:\n        return os.getenv(\"DB_PASSWORD\", \"\").strip()\n\n    @property\n    def database_url(self) -\u003e str:\n        # postgresql://user:pass@host:port/db\n        return f\"postgresql://{self.db_user}:{self.db_password}@{self.db_host}:{self.db_port}/{self.db_name}\"\n\n    # YAML\n    @property\n    def agents_config(self) -\u003e dict:\n        return self._config.get(\"agents\", {})\n\n    @property\n    def models_config(self) -\u003e dict:\n        return self._config.get(\"models\", {})\n\n    @property\n    def schedule_config(self) -\u003e dict:\n        return self._config.get(\"schedule\", {})\n\n    def validate(self) -\u003e dict:\n        issues = []\n        if not self.telegram_bot_token:\n            issues.append(\"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN eksik\")\n        if not self.gemini_api_key:\n            issues.append(\"GEMINI_API_KEY eksik\")\n        if not self.db_user:\n            issues.append(\"DB_USER eksik\")\n        if not self.db_password:\n            issues.append(\"DB_PASSWORD eksik\")\n        return {\"ok\": len(issues) == 0, \"issues\": issues}\n\nsettings = Settings()\nEOF\n\n# config/logging_config.py\ncat \u003e config/logging_config.py \u003c\u003c'EOF'\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom loguru import logger\n\nBASE_DIR = Path(__file__).resolve().parent.parent\nLOG_DIR = BASE_DIR / \"logs\"\nLOG_DIR.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n\ndef setup_logging(level: str = \"INFO\"):\n    logger.remove()\n\n    logger.add(\n        sys.stdout,\n        level=level,\n        format=\"{time:YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss} | {level:\u003c8} | {name}:{function}:{line} | {message}\"\n    )\n\n    logger.add(\n        LOG_DIR / \"system_{time:YYYY-MM-DD}.log\",\n        level=\"DEBUG\",\n        rotation=\"00:00\",\n        retention=\"14 days\",\n        compression=\"zip\",\n        encoding=\"utf-8\",\n        format=\"{time:YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss} | {level:\u003c8} | {name}:{function}:{line} | {message}\",\n    )\n\n    return logger\nEOF\n\n# config/agents_config.yaml (planla uyumlu minimal)\ncat \u003e config/agents_config.yaml \u003c\u003c'EOF'\nschedule:\n  morning_meeting:\n    hour: 9\n    minute: 0\n    days: \"mon-fri\"\n\nagents:\n  ceo:\n    model: \"gemini-flash\"\n    skill_file: \"agents/prompts/ceo.txt\"\n\n  scanner:\n    model: \"gemini-flash\"\n    skill_file: \"agents/prompts/scanner.txt\"\n\n  news:\n    model: \"gemini-flash\"\n    skill_file: \"agents/prompts/news.txt\"\n\n  strategy:\n    model: \"gemini-pro\"\n    skill_file: \"agents/prompts/strategy.txt\"\n\nmodels:\n  gemini-flash:\n    provider: \"google\"\n    model_name: \"gemini-2.0-flash\"\n    fallback: \"groq-llama\"\n\n  gemini-pro:\n    provider: \"google\"\n    model_name: \"gemini-2.0-pro\"\n    fallback: \"gemini-flash\"\n\n  groq-llama:\n    provider: \"groq\"\n    model_name: \"llama-3.1-70b-versatile\"\nEOF\n\n# core/modules/database.py (gerekli tablolar + create_tables + health_check)\ncat \u003e core/modules/database.py \u003c\u003c'EOF'\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nfrom datetime import datetime, date\nfrom sqlalchemy import (\n    create_engine, text, Column, Integer, String, Float, DateTime, Boolean, Text, JSON, Date\n)\nfrom sqlalchemy.orm import sessionmaker, declarative_base\nfrom sqlalchemy.pool import QueuePool\nfrom loguru import logger\n\nfrom config.settings import settings\n\nBase = declarative_base()\n\n# --- Minimal ama gerekli tablolar ---\n\nclass PriceCache(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"price_cache\"\n    ticker = Column(String(32), primary_key=True)   # örn: d:THYAO / w:THYAO\n    fetched_at = Column(Date, nullable=False)\n    data = Column(Text, nullable=False)\n\nclass WatchlistItem(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"watchlist\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    chat_id = Column(String(64), nullable=False, index=True)\n    ticker = Column(String(20), nullable=False, index=True)\n    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass EmaSettings(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"ema_settings\"\n    ticker = Column(String(20), primary_key=True)\n    daily_fast = Column(Integer, default=9)\n    daily_slow = Column(Integer, default=21)\n    weekly_fast = Column(Integer, default=9)\n    weekly_slow = Column(Integer, default=21)\n    updated_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow, onupdate=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass ScanResult(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"scan_results\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    scan_date = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow, nullable=False)\n    chat_id = Column(String(64), nullable=False, index=True)\n    strategy_code = Column(String(10), nullable=False)\n    symbol = Column(String(20), nullable=False, index=True)\n\n    price_at_signal = Column(Float)\n    indicators = Column(JSON)           # RSI, RVOL, vs.\n    signal_strength = Column(Float)     # confidence/composite\n    ai_interpretation = Column(Text)\n\n    # Öğrenme için (sonradan doldurulacak)\n    ret_1d = Column(Float)\n    ret_5d = Column(Float)\n    ret_21d = Column(Float)\n    outcome_filled = Column(Boolean, default=False)\n\n    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass TradeBook(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"trade_book\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    chat_id = Column(String(64), nullable=False, index=True)\n    symbol = Column(String(20), nullable=False, index=True)\n    side = Column(String(10), nullable=False)  # BUY / SELL\n    price = Column(Float, nullable=False)\n    quantity = Column(Float, nullable=False)\n    reason = Column(Text)\n    strategy_ref = Column(String(32))\n\n    trade_date = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n    pnl = Column(Float)\n    pnl_percentage = Column(Float)\n    hold_days = Column(Integer)\n    ai_review = Column(Text)\n\n    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass OpenPosition(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"open_positions\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    chat_id = Column(String(64), nullable=False, index=True)\n    symbol = Column(String(20), nullable=False, index=True)\n    avg_price = Column(Float, nullable=False)\n    quantity = Column(Float, nullable=False)\n    reason = Column(Text)\n    opened_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n    updated_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow, onupdate=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass AgentDecision(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"agent_decisions\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    agent_name = Column(String(50), nullable=False)\n    decision_type = Column(String(50), nullable=False)\n    context = Column(JSON)\n    decision = Column(Text, nullable=False)\n    confidence = Column(Float)\n    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass MarketContext(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"market_context\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    context_date = Column(Date, unique=True, nullable=False)\n    regime = Column(String(32))\n    key_news_summary = Column(Text)\n    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass LessonLearned(Base):\n    __tablename__ = \"lessons_learned\"\n    id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)\n    lesson_date = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n    source = Column(String(50))\n    category = Column(String(50))\n    lesson = Column(Text, nullable=False)\n    evidence = Column(JSON)\n    importance = Column(Integer, default=5)\n    is_active = Column(Boolean, default=True)\n    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow)\n\nclass DatabaseManager:\n    _instance = None\n\n    def __new__(cls):\n        if cls._instance is None:\n            cls._instance = super().__new__(cls)\n            cls._instance._init()\n        return cls._instance\n\n    def _init(self):\n        self.engine = create_engine(\n            settings.database_url,\n            poolclass=QueuePool,\n            pool_size=5,\n            max_overflow=10,\n            pool_pre_ping=True,\n            echo=False,\n        )\n        self.Session = sessionmaker(bind=self.engine)\n\n    def create_tables(self):\n        Base.metadata.create_all(self.engine)\n\n    def health_check(self) -\u003e dict:\n        try:\n            with self.engine.connect() as conn:\n                conn.execute(text(\"SELECT 1\")).fetchone()\n            return {\"ok\": True}\n        except Exception as e:\n            return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": str(e)}\n\n    def session(self):\n        return self.Session()\n\ndb = DatabaseManager()\nEOF\n\n# memory/agent_memory.py (agent hafıza wrapper)\ncat \u003e memory/agent_memory.py \u003c\u003c'EOF'\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nfrom datetime import datetime, date\nfrom loguru import logger\nfrom core.modules.database import db, AgentDecision, LessonLearned, MarketContext\n\nclass AgentMemory:\n    def log_decision(self, agent_name: str, decision_type: str, decision: str,\n                     context: dict | None = None, confidence: float | None = None):\n        s = db.session()\n        try:\n            rec = AgentDecision(\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                decision_type=decision_type,\n                decision=decision,\n                context=context or {},\n                confidence=confidence\n            )\n            s.add(rec)\n            s.commit()\n        except Exception as e:\n            s.rollback()\n            logger.error(f\"AgentDecision kayıt hatası: {e}\")\n        finally:\n            s.close()\n\n    def get_active_lessons(self, limit: int = 10, category: str | None = None):\n        s = db.session()\n        try:\n            q = s.query(LessonLearned).filter(LessonLearned.is_active == True)  # noqa\n            if category:\n                q = q.filter(LessonLearned.category == category)\n            return q.order_by(LessonLearned.importance.desc()).limit(limit).all()\n        finally:\n            s.close()\n\n    def upsert_market_context(self, context_date: date, regime: str | None = None,\n                              key_news_summary: str | None = None):\n        s = db.session()\n        try:\n            rec = s.query(MarketContext).filter(MarketContext.context_date == context_date).first()\n            if rec is None:\n                rec = MarketContext(context_date=context_date, regime=regime, key_news_summary=key_news_summary)\n                s.add(rec)\n            else:\n                if regime is not None:\n                    rec.regime = regime\n                if key_news_summary is not None:\n                    rec.key_news_summary = key_news_summary\n            s.commit()\n        except Exception as e:\n            s.rollback()\n            logger.error(f\"MarketContext upsert hatası: {e}\")\n        finally:\n            s.close()\n\nmemory = AgentMemory()\nEOF\n\n# core/orchestrator/event_manager.py (placeholder - sonraki adımda dolduracağız)\ncat \u003e core/orchestrator/event_manager.py \u003c\u003c'EOF'\n\"\"\"\nZamanlanmış işlerin orkestrasyonu (